{"tid":331115,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[動物奇觀] 蘇格蘭 Bass Rock一遊","createTime":"2017-07-22T00:06:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-22T04:46:34.000Z","uid":129865,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"618e97d0969fa6b8dffe53c2cf2bac184ac2cf00","tid":331115,"uid":129865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T00:06:20.000Z","msg":"上年6月小弟一條友去英國旅行,係蘇格蘭嘅時候去咗一個叫Bass Rock可以見到好多雀仔仲比Sir David Attenborough 稱讚為 &quot;one of the wildlife wonders of the world&quot;嘅地方<br />\n唔多覺有post提起過, 相唔多但同大家分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw 由於部相機太廢, 小弟手震, 天氣差加埋大部分相都係船上面影,D相都幾核突下, 請大家手下留情,屌細力D <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   <br />\n今次亦係小弟第一次寫遊記, 悶親大家/寫到1999咁還請各位見諒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁話說去Scotland去晒所有想去嘅景點之後,仲有一整日空閒時間<br />\n正苦惱點樣打發時間之際, 係住個間酒店見到Scottish Seabird Centre 嘅leaflet, 見到佢地有搞去Bass Rock 嘅 boat trip,可以見到D唔錯嘅雀 <br />\n咁本身小弟係大學都係讀依個範疇嘅野,平時係香港都間中會出去睇下雀, 反正無其他地方想去, 一於Let's GO !!<br />\n<br />\n朝早起身食個包後去Edinburgh Waverley搭火車去North Berwick<br />\n個天灰濛濛一片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/22/010131_4da8a4d9dabd23d8c0990cafdac22908.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F22%2F010131_4da8a4d9dabd23d8c0990cafdac22908.jpg&h=e1d656b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n落車後行去海邊<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/22/010410_a65693d8a9a4bcee6df760bac33da79e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F22%2F010410_a65693d8a9a4bcee6df760bac33da79e.jpg&h=faa2102f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/22/010419_33268e646ce7a5d4552ba8ef43e646c8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F22%2F010419_33268e646ce7a5d4552ba8ef43e646c8.jpg&h=eaab2700&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後就會見到Scottish Seabird Centre <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/22/010858_b2bac75940ada0a2e7c3f500eda2f727.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F22%2F010858_b2bac75940ada0a2e7c3f500eda2f727.jpg&h=02283166&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(太興奮唔記得影個centre,上圖取自互聯網)<br />\n<br />\nWalk in報Boat trip好彩仲有位, 記住要上官網查船期(每日時間唔同)如果怕full可以 book定先~<br />\n順帶一提, centre入面有個展覽館, 要額外比多少少錢但幾多野睇<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/22/011204_5f74d431c1d1548bd616bf5885b83527.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F22%2F011204_5f74d431c1d1548bd616bf5885b83527.jpg&h=cbbc0b01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n開船了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/22/011312_17026eba94e4a769bbd5bc0a3b9725a0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F22%2F011312_17026eba94e4a769bbd5bc0a3b9725a0.jpg&h=9246a65d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n到達Bass Rock之前部船會先去附近另一個叫Craigleith嘅島仔, 雀數量唔太多, 部船亦唔會行得太埋,勉強見到幾種海鷗同刀嘴海雀 Razorbill咁<br />\n<br />\n<strong>刀嘴海雀 Razorbill</strong> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/22/020244_76830a63d4e25f063b67914f1666d83b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F22%2F020244_76830a63d4e25f063b67914f1666d83b.jpg&h=2b6d3945&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n...過左一陣, 有發現!<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/22/012802_2cc2c5302b18dc11933ae4fbf74df4a6.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F22%2F012802_2cc2c5302b18dc11933ae4fbf74df4a6.JPG&h=9fdad234&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今次個 trip嘅 前菜:    <br />\n<strong>北極海鸚 Atlantic Puffin </strong>  <del>小丑雀</del><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/22/013003_47073aa32a7c39699f7f4abb5ca463c0.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F22%2F013003_47073aa32a7c39699f7f4abb5ca463c0.JPG&h=db49482d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/22/013254_60bd97cd99ec0f32071c7470c3962622.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F22%2F013254_60bd97cd99ec0f32071c7470c3962622.jpg&h=d06f4b8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(上: 取自互聯網   下:centre入面live cam畫面)<br />\n<br />\n雖然係英國棲息嘅海鸚唔算太多, D雀仲要離部船好遠<br />\n但成團人都依然好興奮  &quot;Oh wow~, Oh cool~, Amazing~&quot;咁 <br />\n前菜食完, 一輪興奮過後, 部船離開Craigleith駛往真正目的地--Bass Rock <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n(心跳加速)<br />\n越黎越接近目的地......開始多雀......P <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/22/014430_db6cf9400d3490284100778976ac6b35.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F22%2F014430_db6cf9400d3490284100778976ac6b35.jpg&h=fb043f38&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/22/014638_8444f29ff4f97c5345f78cbba3d7c26f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F22%2F014638_8444f29ff4f97c5345f78cbba3d7c26f.jpg&h=80e2c9c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">到達</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/22/014856_8a33757a91b676f11518320236f630b6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F22%2F014856_8a33757a91b676f11518320236f630b6.jpg&h=fd730565&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n島上面所有白點都係雀 X 3<br />\n重要所以要講三次!<br />\n<br />\n真面目:<strong>北方塘鵝 Northern Gannet</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/22/015141_aed1754474c87b2670430d5a0bc2fd6e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F22%2F015141_aed1754474c87b2670430d5a0bc2fd6e.jpg&h=f4a32985&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n每年冬天係近赤道地區避開嚴寒後, 由二月開始番去Bass Rock繁殖, 六七八月左右見到最多<br />\nBass Rock依個只有3萬平方米嘅島仔上面可以搵到北方塘鵝全世界最大嘅colony (依種雀全球六成&quot;鳥口&quot;)<br />\n最高峰可以有超過十萬隻雀同幾萬個巢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 相當震撼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nMore相:<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/22/020459_f7a8247206679f5d1df7e4ae62f980d0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F22%2F020459_f7a8247206679f5d1df7e4ae62f980d0.jpg&h=2811a071&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/22/020611_76314c7aae39ce96cc8036b4bc326df9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F22%2F020611_76314c7aae39ce96cc8036b4bc326df9.jpg&h=309fd20a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/22/021245_f134f11eeae5ed71b095806ac7a7ac50.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F22%2F021245_f134f11eeae5ed71b095806ac7a7ac50.jpg&h=1f627aa2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/22/021603_7d1a1eb1aaac67271afd643aa0704271.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F22%2F021603_7d1a1eb1aaac67271afd643aa0704271.jpg&h=80d827ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/22/021853_385014927109e521c9f78f159e70c13e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F22%2F021853_385014927109e521c9f78f159e70c13e.jpg&h=61c1db1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n現場睇遠比睇相壯觀一百倍<br />\n各位就算唔係wildlife lover, 有時間都不妨去探下佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n多謝大家收睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"897bb165513f65b236e7dfd115d31e10f0e1dce7","tid":331115,"uid":18624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T04:02:39.000Z","msg":"呢度係edingbrugh 再上？"},{"pid":"d91a72a9a4237f746384b10c2fba8654a9340c20","tid":331115,"uid":129865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T04:40:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢度係edingbrugh 再上？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n東面"},{"pid":"c8739ac7bb30540a854686ac0f0ae07849ddfbbe","tid":331115,"uid":129865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T04:46:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/22/124531_b5cbed784fb93e57925a2939da1710fc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F22%2F124531_b5cbed784fb93e57925a2939da1710fc.jpg&h=61c7c12a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nEdinburgh坐火車大約半個鐘頭左右就到North Berwick"}]}